description: Our goal is simply, to offer our customers the wholesome goodness of Taiwanese & Vietnamese cooking by using freshest ingredients in our food prepared daily!Tainamite was established in 2010 by Michael. Some might ask: what does Tainamite mean? It is a combination of three elements: Taiwanese, Vietnamese, and Dynamite. Their goal is simply: To offer wholesome goodness of Taiwanese and Vietnamese home style cooking by using the freshest ingredients prepared daily. Through Tainamite, Michael brings Asian flavors to the melting pot of Southern California. Perhaps you have tried Taiwanese and Vietnamese food in restaurants, but they have integrated their own flavors to change the traditional to untraditional.Tainamite's mission is to build a long-term relationship with its customers, venders, and suppliers. Your support, comments and suggestions, and feedback are always welcome, therefore, Tainamite can grow and serve you better in every possible way. Until then, keep being dynamic and enjoy all the Taiwanese and Vietnamese food that Tainamite has to offer.Tainamite
name: Tainamite
